name: Cloud Vapes
description:
These are portable vaporizers that are made for taking concentrate hits while on the go (works BEST with wax).

Comes with a USB charger and has a LIFETIME warranty on batteries.

Replacement cartridges are also available.

name: Vaped State Elite Kits
description:
Portable vaporizers that are made for vaping almost anything smokeable. These are capable of providing BIG hits from concentrates, flowers, kief, and hash.

The kit comes with:
1. eGo ctwist 650mAh battery
2. CE5 liquid tank (made for ejuice,canna oil,nic juice)
3. Flower chamber 
4. Wax chamber that also will work with herb at a higher volt! 
5. Case
6. USB charger


30 day warranty for factory damaged products.

name: Prefilled Ejuice
description:
The cartridges come filled with 1mg of ejuice which is good for anywhere from 120-200 puffs depending on how you use it. 

Email or kik us for more information and flavors
